==Early life== Andrea Colli was born 15 June 1966.<ref name="bocconibio">{{cite web|title=ANDREA COLLI|url=http://faculty.unibocconi.eu/andreacolli/|website=Bocconi University|accessdate=May 12, 2017}}</ref> He graduated from Bocconi University, where he also earned a PhD in Economic and Social History.<ref name="bocconibio"/>
==Career== Colli is a Professor of Business History, Head of Department of Social and Political sciences at his alma mater, Bocconi University.<ref name="bocconibio"/> He was a visiting professor at the [[Lancaster University Management School]].<ref name="lancasterbio">{{cite web|title=Professor Andrea Colli|url=http://www.lancaster.ac.uk/lums/people/andrea-colli|website=Lancaster University Management School|accessdate=May 12, 2017}}</ref>
